# Privacy Policy for BSDGo

BSDGo values and respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how your data is handled when using the app.

---

## 1. Information Collection

**BSDGo does not collect, store, or transmit** any personal information or user data to external servers.

---

## 2. Location Access

BSDGo requests location access **solely to determine your proximity to BSD Link bus stops**. This information is processed **entirely on-device** and is never stored, transmitted, or shared.

---

## 3. Data Storage

BSDGo does **not store any user data** outside of standard iOS system frameworks. All runtime data is handled temporarily within the app session and **remains on the user‚Äôs device**.

---

## 4. Third-Party Services

BSDGo does **not use** any third-party analytics, advertising networks, or tracking technologies.

---

## 5. Changes to This Policy

This Privacy Policy may be updated periodically. Any changes will be reflected by updating the **‚ÄúEffective Date‚Äù** listed below.

---

